878
00:35:13,070 --> 00:35:14,340
This fire attack

879
00:35:14,780 --> 00:35:15,890
must succeed.

880
00:35:16,540 --> 00:35:19,130
If anyone makes a mistake

881
00:35:19,230 --> 00:35:21,330
at any point,

882
00:35:21,670 --> 00:35:23,070
it will be unforgivable.

883
00:35:23,260 --> 00:35:24,600
