886
00:35:31,850 --> 00:35:33,430
I'll come in a couple of days

887
00:35:33,430 --> 00:35:35,640
to announce the specific plan.

888
00:35:45,800 --> 00:35:46,590
Shrike,

889
00:35:47,260 --> 00:35:49,230
you're ruthless.

890
00:35:58,680 --> 00:36:03,380
